                    <span>This book clearly teaches and demonstrates, with real-world examples, how to develop powerfull add-ins for Visual Studio.NET. <br>This book is a great resource for .NET starters - in regards to Add-ins - and a fantasic reference for experts.<br>Serious .NET developers should definatelly add this book to their library.</span>
                  
              
